  • Classes in Part2 used by Part2
    Class Description
    BadIsbn10Exception
    The BadIsbn10Exception is a custom exception class designed to be invoked when a book record contains an invalid 10-digit ISBN number.
    BadIsbn13Exception
    The BadIsbn13Exception is a custom exception class designed to be invoked when a book record contains an invalid 13-digit ISBN number.
    BadIsbnException
    The BadIsbnException is a custom exception class designed to be invoked when a book record contains a generally invalid ISBN number.
    BadPriceException
    The BadPriceException is a custom exception class designed to be invoked when a book record contains negative value in the price field.
    BadYearException
    The BadYearException is a custom exception class designed to be invoked when a book record contains an invalid year.
